{"tid":1918467,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內閣官房長官菅義偉：日本未需要進入緊急狀態","createTime":"2020-03-10T06:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T06:32:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e863bc45f2862b1826f026546b87f40932cb1380","tid":1918467,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:31:14.000Z","msg":"日本內閣會議通過法案，容許首相安倍晉三在必要情況下宣布國家進入緊急狀態，將提交國會審議。<br />\n<br />\n內閣官房長官菅義偉說，日本目前情況未需要宣布進入緊急狀態，但認為基於風險管理，為最壞情況做好充分準備，十分重要。他承認政府需要一個更高程度的法律框架，包括有權宣布進入緊急狀態，以減輕新型肺炎爆發帶來的影響，強調政府在作出有關決定前，會小心考慮措施對人民生活的影響。<br />\n<br />\n根據法案，日本一旦進入緊急狀態，地方政府可以指示當地居民留在室內，並要求學校停課及取消活動。政府還可以要求藥物和食品供應商提供基本物資，以及臨時接管私人土地和設施，用作提供醫療服務。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513537-20200310.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513537-20200310.htm&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSipZd1NrJsyKidS%2BVLva3MM%3D&h=2b1e548a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513537-20200310.htm&h=246ceb36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513537-20200310.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bd1aa9b7c95172ce6d4c70d618ea1657b1fc0261","tid":1918467,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0899010a37dd753e74f68f5e2dad2323c07da0","tid":1918467,"uid":60297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:32:40.000Z","msg":"睇錯日本妹"}]}